### Dynamic Inventory — AWS EC2 Plugin (NovaMart Pattern)

```yaml
# inventory/aws_ec2.yml
# This file IS the dynamic inventory — Ansible recognizes the plugin name
plugin: amazon.aws.aws_ec2

# AWS regions to query
regions:
  - us-east-1
  - us-west-2
  - eu-west-1

